- Incomplete integration that breaks existing systems
- Lost progress and knowledge gaps

**FORBIDDEN SHORTCUTS:**
- ‚ùå Skipping IDENTIFY step and assuming nothing exists
- ‚ùå Building new without VERIFY step testing
- ‚ùå Making decisions without ANALYZE step assessment
- ‚ùå Implementing without TEST step verification
- ‚ùå Completing work without DOCUMENT step tracking

**üèÜ SUCCESS EXAMPLES:**

